          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 0 degree yield of alphas from fluorine has been",
                "compared with the 0 degree recoil proton yield from",
                "alkathene for which the differential cross section is",
                "reported by Fowler and Brolley as 530 mb/sr. With a",
                "knowledge of the effective thicknesses of the",
                "alkathene and teflon targets and hence the number of",
                "hydrogen and fluorine atoms, sigma(0 degree) for",
                "fluorine alphas has been computed."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in the cross section comprises",
                " the counting statistics, the finite angular aperture",
                " which varies from 16 to 4 degree at scattering angles",
                " from 0 to 180 degree, the large uncertainty in the",
                " effective fluorine target thickness particularly at",
                " low alpha energies."
              ]
            }
          ],
